name: Circlepix
0:
”Alexa, ask Circlepix for my PixSocial statistics.”
”Alexa, ask Circlepix about my statistics.”
”Alexa, open Circlepix and get my stats.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: circlepix
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Circlepix allows you to check the number of social media engagements that you've received from your PIXsocial posts during the last week.

This skill requires an active Circlepix account with an active PIXsocial membership.

In order to invoke skill, you must say either "ask" or "open" followed by the word "Circlepix".
